title: 212 - That’s Ziitty Capone
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a FULL BARN as the boys kick it off with chatter about all the boys latest weekend. With a rather candid start, the boys jump right into the Pod FOD which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Todays FOD includes Octopuses confirmed out of this planet, VR’s latest advancements in the kissing game, vin Deisel rumors, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
